---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About" 
  description="Learn about Md Shahnawaz Hussain - Digital Marketing specialist and web developer sharing AI tools and productivity strategies"
>
  <div class="about-page">
    <div class="container">
      <!-- Hero Section -->
      <section class="about-hero fade-in-up">
        <div class="hero-content">
          <div class="hero-text">
            <h1>Hi, I'm <span class="gradient-text">Md Shahnawaz Hussain</span></h1>
            <p class="hero-subtitle">
              A Digital Marketing specialist and FreeCodeCamp certified web developer who's passionate about building AI-powered solutions and sharing practical strategies that actually work for students and professionals.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="hero-stats">
            <div class="stat-box">
              <div class="stat-number">2-3</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Hours per week on this blog</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
              <div class="stat-number">$0-20</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Monthly tool budget</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box">
              <div class="stat-number">100%</div>
              <div class="stat-label">Transparent metrics</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Story Section -->
      <section class="story-section fade-in-up stagger-1">
        <h2>Why This Blog Exists</h2>
        
        <div class="story-grid">
          <div class="story-card">
            <div class="story-icon">😤</div>
            <h3>The Problem</h3>
            <p>
              Most productivity and AI content is written by full-time creators with $500/month tool budgets and 40+ hour work weeks. 
              Their advice doesn't work when you're juggling classes, assignments, and maybe a part-time job.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="story-card">
            <div class="story-icon">💡</div>
            <h3>The Experiment</h3>
            <p>
              I decided to test every productivity hack, AI tool, and side hustle strategy I could find—but with real student constraints: 
              limited time, limited budget, and zero room for expensive mistakes.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="story-card">
            <div class="story-icon">📊</div>
            <h3>The Solution</h3>
            <p>
              This blog is my lab notebook. Every post includes real data: time saved, money spent, what worked, what flopped. 
              No affiliate spam. No "trust me bro" advice. Just transparent experiments.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- What I Focus On -->
      <section class="focus-section fade-in-up stagger-2">
        <h2>What I Write About</h2>
        
        <div class="focus-pillars">
          <div class="pillar">
            <div class="pillar-icon">🤖</div>
            <h3>AI & Automation</h3>
            <p>Using ChatGPT, Claude, and no-code tools to work smarter. Real workflows that save 10+ hours per week.</p>
            <div class="pillar-topics">
              <span>ChatGPT Prompts</span>
              <span>Notion Automation</span>
              <span>AI for Research</span>
              <span>Workflow Optimization</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="pillar">
            <div class="pillar-icon">💼</div>
            <h3>Career Building</h3>
            <p>Portfolio projects, resume optimization, and breaking into tech without a CS degree.</p>
            <div class="pillar-topics">
              <span>Portfolio Projects</span>
              <span>Resume Tips</span>
              <span>Interview Prep</span>
              <span>Freelancing</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="pillar">
            <div class="pillar-icon">💰</div>
            <h3>Side Income</h3>
            <p>Realistic strategies for students to earn their first $500-1,000/month online.</p>
            <div class="pillar-topics">
              <span>Freelancing</span>
              <span>Digital Products</span>
              <span>Affiliate Marketing</span>
              <span>Income Reports</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- My Stack -->
      <section class="stack-section fade-in-up stagger-3">
        <h2>My Current Tech Stack</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">The tools I actually use (and recommend)</p>
        
        <div class="stack-grid">
          <div class="stack-category">
            <h4>💻 Development</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>VS Code (editor)</li>
              <li>Astro (this blog)</li>
              <li>GitHub (version control)</li>
              <li>Netlify (hosting)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="stack-category">
            <h4>🤖 AI & Productivity</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Claude (research & writing)</li>
              <li>ChatGPT (coding help)</li>
              <li>Notion (everything else)</li>
              <li>Zapier free tier (automation)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="stack-category">
            <h4>📊 Analytics & Marketing</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Google Analytics 4</li>
              <li>ConvertKit (email)</li>
              <li>Canva (graphics)</li>
              <li>Gumroad (digital products)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="stack-category">
            <h4>💰 Monetization</h4>
            <ul>
              <li>Affiliate programs (various)</li>
              <li>Gumroad (templates)</li>
              <li>Upwork (freelancing)</li>
              <li>Stripe (coming soon)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Current Projects -->
      <section class="projects-section fade-in-up stagger-4">
        <h2>Current Projects & Experiments</h2>
        
        <div class="projects-list">
          <div class="project-card">
            <div class="project-status active">Active</div>
            <h3>This Blog (AI Student Hub)</h3>
            <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Reach 5,000 monthly visitors and $500/month revenue by month 6</p>
            <p><strong>Current Progress:</strong></p>
            <div class="progress-bar">
              <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 15%"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="project-metrics">
              <span>750 monthly visitors</span>
              <span>•</span>
              <span>$40/month revenue</span>
              <span>•</span>
              <span>Month 3</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="project-card">
            <div class="project-status active">Active</div>
            <h3>AI Productivity Templates</h3>
            <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Create and sell 5 digital products (Notion templates, prompt libraries)</p>
            <p><strong>Current Progress:</strong> 2 products launched, $120 total sales</p>
            <div class="progress-bar">
              <div class="progress-fill" style="width: 40%"></div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="project-card">
            <div class="project-status planned">Planned</div>
            <h3>AI Career Accelerator Course</h3>
            <p><strong>Goal:</strong> Launch a cohort-based course teaching AI productivity to students</p>
            <p><strong>Timeline:</strong> Q4 2026 (after proving concept with blog content)</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Principles -->
      <section class="principles-section fade-in-up stagger-5">
        <h2>My Blogging Principles</h2>
        
        <div class="principles-grid">
          <div class="principle">
            <h4>🎯 1. Transparent Metrics</h4>
            <p>Every experiment includes real numbers. Traffic, revenue, time saved, failure rates—all public.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="principle">
            <h4>💰 2. Free-First</h4>
            <p>I only recommend paid tools when they deliver clear ROI. Most tutorials cost $0-20/month to follow.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="principle">
            <h4>⏱️ 3. Time-Realistic</h4>
            <p>All projects designed for 2-3 hours per week. If it requires more, I'll say so upfront.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="principle">
            <h4>🚫 4. No BS</h4>
            <p>No clickbait. No "secret strategies." No hiding failures. Just what actually works.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="principle">
            <h4>📚 5. Student Perspective</h4>
            <p>Written by someone solving the same problems you face, not a guru selling courses.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="principle">
            <h4>🔨 6. Build-in-Public</h4>
            <p>I share failures, pivots, and learning moments—not just the highlight reel.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- CTA Section -->
      <section class="cta-section fade-in-up stagger-6">
        <div class="cta-box">
          <h2>Want to Follow Along?</h2>
          <p>
            I send weekly updates every Sunday with:
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li>Latest blog posts and experiments</li>
            <li>Transparent metrics (traffic, revenue, time spent)</li>
            <li>AI prompts and productivity tips</li>
            <li>Lessons learned and pivots</li>
          </ul>
          
          <form class="newsletter-form" action="https://formspree.io/f/maqvlowp" method="POST">
            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="mdshahnawazhussain32@gmail.com" required>
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Join 500+ Students</button>
          </form>
          
          <p class="form-note">No spam. Unsubscribe anytime. I respect your inbox.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="social-links">
          <h3>Connect With Me</h3>
          <div class="social-grid">
            <a href="https://twitter.com/yourusername" target="_blank" class="social-link">
              <span class="social-icon">🐦</span>
              <span>Twitter</span>
            </a>
            <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourusername" target="_blank" class="social-link">
              <span class="social-icon">💼</span>
              <span>LinkedIn</span>
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/yourusername" target="_blank" class="social-link">
              <span class="social-icon">💻</span>
              <span>GitHub</span>
            </a>
            <a href="mailto:mdshahnawazhussain32@gmail.com" class="social-link">
              <span class="social-icon">✉️</span>
              <span>Email</span>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style>
.about-page {
  padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
}

/* Hero Section */
.about-hero {
  padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
  text-align: center;
}

.hero-text h1 {
  font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
}

.hero-subtitle {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto var(--space-xl);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.hero-stats {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-lg);
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.stat-box {
  padding: var(--space-lg);
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
}

.stat-number {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--color-primary);
  line-height: 1;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
}

.stat-label {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
}

/* Story Section */
.story-section {
  padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.story-section h2 {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
}

.story-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-lg);
}

.story-card {
  padding: var(--space-xl);
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  text-align: center;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.story-card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  border-color: var(--color-primary);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.1);
}

.story-icon {
  font-size: 3rem;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
}

.story-card h3 {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  color: var(--color-primary);
}

/* Focus Section */
.focus-section {
  padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  margin: var(--space-2xl) 0;
}

.focus-section h2 {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
}

.focus-pillars {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-xl);
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.pillar {
  padding: var(--space-xl);
  background: var(--color-bg);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
}

.pillar-icon {
  font-size: 3rem;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
}

.pillar h3 {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
}

.pillar-topics {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: var(--space-xs);
  margin-top: var(--space-md);
}

.pillar-topics span {
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  padding: 0.25rem 0.5rem;
  background: var(--color-bg-tertiary);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  border-radius: 3px;
  color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
}

/* Stack Section */
.stack-section {
  padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
  max-width: 1000px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.stack-section h2 {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
}

.section-subtitle {
  text-align: center;
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
}

.stack-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-lg);
}

.stack-category {
  padding: var(--space-lg);
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
}

.stack-category h4 {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  color: var(--color-primary);
}

.stack-category ul {
  list-style: none;
  padding: 0;
}

.stack-category li {
  padding: var(--space-xs) 0;
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
}

.stack-category li:last-child {
  border-bottom: none;
}

/* Projects Section */
.projects-section {
  padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.projects-section h2 {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
}

.projects-list {
  display: grid;
  gap: var(--space-lg);
}

.project-card {
  padding: var(--space-xl);
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  position: relative;
}

.project-status {
  position: absolute;
  top: var(--space-md);
  right: var(--space-md);
  padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  border-radius: 3px;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  font-weight: 600;
}

.project-status.active {
  background: var(--color-primary);
  color: var(--color-bg);
}

.project-status.planned {
  background: var(--color-accent-3);
  color: var(--color-bg);
}

.project-card h3 {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
}

.progress-bar {
  height: 8px;
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-radius: 4px;
  overflow: hidden;
  margin: var(--space-md) 0;
}

.progress-fill {
  height: 100%;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-accent-2));
}

.project-metrics {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--space-sm);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
  font-family: var(--font-mono);
}

/* Principles Section */
.principles-section {
  padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  margin: var(--space-2xl) 0;
}

.principles-section h2 {
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
}

.principles-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-lg);
  max-width: 1100px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.principle {
  padding: var(--space-lg);
  background: var(--color-bg);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  border-left: 4px solid var(--color-primary);
}

.principle h4 {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
}

/* CTA Section */
.cta-section {
  padding: var(--space-2xl) 0;
  max-width: 700px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.cta-box {
  padding: var(--space-xl);
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(0, 255, 136, 0.05), rgba(78, 205, 196, 0.05));
  border: 1px solid var(--color-primary);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
}

.cta-box h2 {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
}

.cta-box ul {
  text-align: left;
  max-width: 500px;
  margin: var(--space-lg) auto;
}

.cta-box li {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
}

.newsletter-form {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--space-sm);
  max-width: 500px;
  margin: var(--space-lg) auto;
}

.newsletter-form input {
  flex: 1;
  padding: 0.875rem 1.25rem;
  background: var(--color-bg);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  color: var(--color-text);
  font-family: var(--font-body);
}

.form-note {
  margin-top: var(--space-sm);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: var(--color-text-tertiary);
}

/* Social Links */
.social-links {
  text-align: center;
}

.social-links h3 {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
}

.social-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-md);
}

.social-link {
  padding: var(--space-md);
  background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-radius: var(--border-radius);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-sm);
  justify-content: center;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.social-link:hover {
  background: var(--color-primary);
  color: var(--color-bg);
  border-color: var(--color-primary);
  transform: translateY(-3px);
}

.social-icon {
  font-size: 1.5rem;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .newsletter-form {
    flex-direction: column;
  }
}
</style>
